Title: Series: A Collection of Prints in Imitation of Drawings
Description: The Rest on the Flight into Egypt; facsimile of a drawing; the Virgin seated on the ground, supporting the infant Jesus; St Joseph seated and reading; an angel leading a donkey towards them; after Guido Reni. 1767 Crayon-manner, in brown ink
Curator's comments: For comment on the series see 1902,1011.4071.
